                "subtype": "sidebar",
                "sidebar_type": "additional_lore",
                "sidebar_heading": "Additional Lore",
                "image": {
                    "type": "image",
                    "name": "Additional Lore",
                    "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                },
                "html": "Brain collectors typically hunt alone, yet some adopt morbid cults that include followers who hope to have their own brains harvested by these alien invaders. The Dominion of the Black includes a wide array of monstrous aliens, of which the brain collectors are merely the most commonly encountered on terrestrial worlds. Many of these aliens have affinities for stealing thoughts, inhabiting bodies, or feeding on memories\u2014the focus on the consumption of brains and of identities suggesting disturbing truths about their coalition. "
            }
        ],
